io.github.prolobjectlink.prolog

Interface PrologReference

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<PrologTerm>, PrologElement, PrologTerm

    public interface PrologReference
extends PrologTerm
    PrologReference is a specialized Term with an Object field, representing Prolog references to Java objects (or to null).
    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain
